name: Two Fridas x Two Agamics
description: In two Frida paintings, Kahlo expressed her despair and loneliness with her separation from Diego. The interpretation that I adapted with myself is the iconic red shirt of my childhood on the left, the freedom of being myself and my desire to travel everywhere with the bus I hold in my hand. A me who is aware of the facts and tries to exist by drawing in a world where it is not possible to be myself.
